summary:
I am in the possesion of a Gymnasium diploma and I am currently studying International Pyschology at Erasmus University of Rotterdam. 
I have excellent communication skills and a lot of work experience. 
I have worked in different sectors and I can adapt easily. Always eager to learn and never gives up!
